-- Japan Government to Back Syndicated Loan to Manila Water, Nikkei Reports
-- B y   F e r g u s   M a g u i r e
-- 2010-09-26T21:31:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/japan-government-to-back-syndicated-loan-to-manila-water-nikkei-reports.html
Mizuho Corporate Bank, Sumitomo
Mitsui Banking Corp., and Bank of Tokyo-Mitsubishi UFJ are
participating in a syndicated loan of about $150 million to
Manila Water Co., Nikkei English News said, without citing
anyone.   The state-backed Nippon Export and Investment Insurance
will provide trade insurance for the loan, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fergus Maguire at 
 fmaguire@bloomberg.net  